":28758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"吹大左好多年啦，早十幾年中學讀書果陣就好食"},{"pid":"4592554f3d362d994120b05006cad6f4796062a2","tid":25723,"uid":44030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"我都覺吹太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學都喺嗰頭番<br />\n食左咁多年都唔覺有乜咁特別<br />\n午晚市都一樣"},{"pid":"1b545f80433fdc760d43e037d800444b253118ff","tid":25723,"uid":51670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:06:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都覺吹太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學都喺嗰頭番<br />\n食左咁多年都唔覺有乜咁特別<br />\n午晚市都一樣</blockquote><br />\n午市都唔係"},{"pid":"c8e18cb3559b239a5efe4faaaa7bf9032f34288b","tid":25723,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:07:04.000Z","msg":"陳浩天幫佢賣廣告喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5230f20d266b048120d181955fd7a5cfe8ebf1","tid":25723,"uid":19624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:08:33.000Z","msg":"係幾好食,不過上次食飯隔離有隻勁大隻老鼠, 嚇到班學生走撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6007280a694b7743c525676ef66f965fbfafa5e9","tid":25723,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:15:40.000Z","msg":"真係好食喎<br />\n利申食過幾次"},{"pid":"db88f9924da96050cb5797b7c2a56ece4b7652d1","tid":25723,"uid":12253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:18:42.000Z","msg":"真心好食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e0853011ce9c64ce9a09c1f0705b11fd2608c4","tid":25723,"uid":57800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"都係普通大排擋, 冇乜特別"},{"pid":"8cb40ba9187b72bc6109ed7d81bc897d15369696","tid":25723,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係吹大咗<br />\n呢一兩年搞到我5:30去都冇位"},{"pid":"e6799e572a639f22e7f2c5cabdfa6af8cd142d8b","tid":25723,"uid":6313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:20:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同陳雲根一樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e5848b288bcfe34389218de21a02f3faf0ad15","tid":25723,"uid":24775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:23:01.000Z","msg":"因為袋家好少大排檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d8c99fc71b2c12928378b6da5db2deccf6ce8e","tid":25723,"uid":8596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:23:11.000Z","msg":"以前食佢真係幾好，午市碟頭飯多選擇而且好夠鑊氣，味道唔差而且平附近商場一半。晚市如果叫小菜一班人飲酒都幾正，不過d粥好唔掂，咩粥都好似白粥溝餸冇乜味而且完全唔綿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10f89c8e3c289b7ea260ac8f8bfbfa58e80b41e","tid":25723,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:32:44.000Z","msg":"新廣發屌打佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f918a65c17bf38ad1f6bab38205c15f697947ff0","tid":25723,"uid":46680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:34:11.000Z","msg":"間間大牌檔都係咁撚上下㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n戇鳩先會吹捧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60785f364190ef1d13b018d31eb7f141a4ed80bc","tid":25723,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:35:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>間間大牌檔都係咁撚上下㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n戇鳩先會吹捧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吹到香港第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8515b175f9f99ba7a2a48c84e7ea2a4c242b3134","tid":25723,"uid":46680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:39:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>間間大牌檔都係咁撚上下㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n戇鳩先會吹捧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吹到香港第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最鳩憎人吹棒一間食店天上有地下無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其此就係$30 藍色雪榚，$40一底雞蛋仔<br />\n<br />\n戇鳩先會曬撚埋晒呢d錢食d成本咁低又唔需要咩技術，純粹為左打卡既戇鳩食品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}